{"tid":244583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳李嘉誠正研出售痴撚線公司 作價最少78億","createTime":"2017-05-15T14:09:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-15T15:03:11.000Z","uid":81617,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2d31c1cf9dae71e76627c81d9796ab888a7cc357","tid":244583,"uid":81617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T14:09:00.000Z","msg":"據彭博引述消息報道，李嘉誠正研究其香港固網電訊業務的各種可能方案，包括可能將其出售。此前九倉吳光正，亦已公佈Cut有線（1097）細節。<br />\n<br />\n據報道，李嘉誠在評估潛在買家對和記環球電訊（HGC）的興趣，售價或不低於10億美元（約78億港元）。不過，報道又提到，李嘉誠不排除繼續持有該業務。該公司通過其香港光纖網絡為企業客戶提供服務。<br />\n<br />\n和記環球電訊屬和記電訊（215）旗下，和記電訊去年固網業務收入41.3億元，EBITDA為12.5億元。<br />\n<br />\n全球十大投行中，有9間為和記環球電訊客戶，另外，主要香港政府部門、公立醫院均為其客戶。集團光纖寬頻網絡覆蓋全港180萬家庭。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170515&amp;guid=56696888&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170515%26guid%3D56696888%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=b83d07b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170515%26guid%3D56696888%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant&h=5bd7476d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170515&amp;guid=56696888&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"49f63843effb54700cb303e5f0aee7f22c7b9406","tid":244583,"uid":81617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T14:10:18.000Z","msg":"Angle方加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"868b83347b365c7d472bb56301bd41d64aea28ce","tid":244583,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T14:10:26.000Z","msg":"Angel方加"},{"pid":"ddd5767f5a8e4bb8be5a7005d544b16083cd3614","tid":244583,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T14:13:22.000Z","msg":"姜呀!姜太公個姜呀!